    GatewayCtrl -->|creates| NetworkPolicyCR["NetworkPolicy"]

    %% Monitoring controller creates resources
    MonitoringCtrl -->|creates| MonStack["MonitoringStack"]
    MonitoringCtrl -->|creates| ThanosQ["ThanosQuerier"]
    MonitoringCtrl -->|creates| Tempo["TempoMonolithic"]
    MonitoringCtrl -->|creates| OTelCollector["OpenTelemetry<br/>Collector"]
    MonitoringCtrl -->|creates| PersesDash["Perses Dashboards"]

    %% External dependencies
    GatewayCtrl -->|depends on| OCP_GW["OpenShift Gateway<br/>API Controller"]
    GatewayCtrl -->|depends on| Istio["Istio / Service Mesh"]
    AuthCtrl -->|depends on| OAuthServer["OpenShift OAuth Server"]
    OperatorManager -->|depends on| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server"]

    %% Webhook
    K8sAPI -->|validates via| WebhookServer

